data.description: WE NEED TO GET THIS SOLD ASAP! BRING ALL OFFERS! Perfect home for a first time home buyer! This cozy, cute, 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom, 1 car garage home has just what you need! Fully fenced in back yard, new roof in 2023, new AC in 2018, new hot water heater in 2019 and new flooring in 2023! This place is literally ready for you to move in and enjoy! The area has several new construction homes and a lot of maintained older homes as well! There is a very rural feel with oak trees and homes on larger parcels! You are also close to famous Blue Springs and the ECO biking trail!
